Timothy Beckley

Synchronicities surround us all, what are these bizarre moments and what can they tell us about the experience of life? Are we really bumping headlong into alternate worlds & realities or does it go deeper.
We take a fascinating look at this phenomena and offer new insights and ideas into some reality shattering experiences.
